sentence: SEC Comment: In the section entitled Fund Summaries-Fees and Expenses with respect to the Ariel Focus Fund in the Prospectus, please (i) change Net Expenses to Total Annual Fund Operating Expenses After Fee Waiver and/or Expense Reimbursement, (ii) confirm that the Adviser does not recoup amounts waived or reimbursed, and (iii) in the footnote to the fee table please state who may terminate the agreement and under what circumstances.
